---
layout: base.njk
titulo: In-Ears KZ y QKZ — ARMS Music Guatemala
seoTitulo: "In-Ears KZ en Guatemala — KZ, QKZ y CCA | ARMS Music"
seoDescripcion: "In-ears KZ y QKZ en Guatemala. Los mejores IEMs al mejor precio. Pago contra entrega, envíos a todo el país."
ogType: "website"
permalink: /in-ears/index.html
---

{# ================================================================
   PÁGINA PILAR — In-Ears. Estructura 100% fiel a Impact:
   1. collection-banner (banner con imagen + título + featured product)
   2. image-link-blocks (subcategorías: accesorios, cables, etc.)
   3. main-collection (grid product-list, sin toolbar de filtros)

   Lógica de datos INTACTA: for prod in productos.inears, varId,
   btnId, prodUrl (filtro productoUrl), include card-producto.njk.
   El toolbar/facets de Impact se omite por completo (decisión ARMS).
================================================================= #}

<main>

  {# ── 1. COLLECTION-BANNER ─────────────────────────────────── #}
  <div class="section section-blends section-full text-custom section--no-top-gap" style="--text-color: 255 255 255;">
    <image-banner reveal-on-scroll="true" parallax="0.3" class="collection-banner content-over-media content-over-media--md full-bleed text-custom" style="--text-color: 255 255 255;">
      <picture>
        {# TODO: imagen de fondo del banner In-Ears (pendiente) #}
        <source media="(max-width: 699px)" srcset="/assets/img/pilar/banner-mobile.webp" width="1300" height="1500">
        <img src="/assets/img/pilar/banner.webp" alt="" width="3200" height="1600" fetchpriority="high">
      </picture>
      <div class="place-self-center arms-text-center sm:place-self-center-start sm:arms-text-start">
        <div class="v-stack gap-4 sm:gap-6">
          <h1 class="h0" reveal-on-scroll="true"><split-lines>In-Ears</split-lines></h1>
          <div class="prose">
            <span>Monitores in-ear KZ, QKZ y CCA al mejor precio de Guatemala. Sonido de alta fidelidad, construcción premium y pago contra entrega en todo el país.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="place-self-end hidden md:block">
        {# FEATURED PRODUCT: KZ Castor Pro — se busca en la data por id.
           TODO: si el id real del Castor Pro no contiene "castor",
           ajusta la condición de abajo. #}
        {% set fp = null %}
        {% for p in productos.inears %}
          {% if "castor" in p.id %}{% set fp = p %}{% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
        {% if fp %}
        {% set fpUrl = fp.id | productoUrl %}
        <div class="collection-featured-product">
          <p class="collection-featured-product__title text-xs bold">Producto destacado</p>
          <div class="horizontal-product horizontal-product--sm rounded-xs snap-start">
            <a href="{{ fpUrl }}" class="collection-featured-product__content"></a>
            <a href="{{ fpUrl }}">
              <img src="/assets/img/productos/{{ fp.imagenes[0] }}" alt="{{ fp.nombre }}" width="800" height="800" loading="lazy" class="horizontal-product__image rounded-xs"
                onerror="this.replaceWith(document.getElementById('svg-tmpl-fp-{{ fp.id }}').content.cloneNode(true))">
            </a>
            <div class="horizontal-product__info">
              <div class="v-stack gap-0.5">
                <span class="text-sm bold">{{ fp.nombre }}</span>
                <price-list class="price-list">
                  {% if fp.precioOriginal %}<s class="text-subdued text-sm">{{ fp.precioOriginal | gtq }}</s>{% endif %}
                  <span class="text-sm{% if fp.precioOriginal %} text-on-sale{% endif %}">{{ fp.precio | gtq }}</span>
                </price-list>
              </div>
            </div>
            <template id="svg-tmpl-fp-{{ fp.id }}">{% include "svgs/" + fp.svgTipo + ".njk" %}</template>
          </div>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </image-banner>
  </div>

  {# ── 2. IMAGE-LINK-BLOCKS (subcategorías) ─────────────────── #}
  <div class="section section-blends section--no-top-gap">
    <image-link-blocks class="image-link-blocks scroll-area bleed md:unbleed">

      {% set subcats = [
        { titulo: "Accesorios In-Ears", url: "/accesorios-inears/", img: "accesorios-inears" },
        { titulo: "Cables", url: "/audio-cables/", img: "cables" },
        { titulo: "Interfaces", url: "/audio-interfaces/", img: "interfaces" },
        { titulo: "Micrófonos", url: "/audio-microfonos/", img: "microfonos" }
      ] %}

      {% for sc in subcats %}
      <div class="image-link-blocks__item group arms-rounded bg-secondary text-custom" style="--text-color: 255 255 255;">
        <a href="{{ sc.url }}" class="content-over-media arms-rounded" style="--content-over-media-overlay: 0 0 0 / 0.0">
          {# TODO: imagen de subcategoría (pendiente) #}
          <img src="/assets/img/subpilar/{{ sc.img }}.webp" alt="{{ sc.titulo }}" width="1200" height="1200" loading="lazy" class="zoom-image">
          <div class="place-self-end-start w-full bold">
            <div class="h-stack justify-between gap-2">
              {{ sc.titulo }}
              <svg role="presentation" focusable="false" width="24" height="24" class="icon icon-circle-button-right-clipped reverse-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M12 24c6.627 0 12-5.373 12-12S18.627 0 12 0 0 5.373 0 12s5.373 12 12 12ZM10.47 9.53 12.94 12l-2.47 2.47 1.06 1.06 3-3 .53-.53-.53-.53-3-3-1.06 1.06Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}

    </image-link-blocks>
  </div>

  {# ── 3. MAIN-COLLECTION (grid de productos, sin toolbar) ──── #}
  <div class="section section-blends">
    <div class="container">
      <product-list class="product-list">
        {% for prod in productos.inears %}
        {% set varId = ("var-cat-" + prod.nombre) | replace(" ", "-") | replace("/", "-") %}
        {% set btnId = ("btn-cat-" + prod.nombre) | replace(" ", "-") | replace("/", "-") %}
        {% set prodUrl = prod.id | productoUrl %}
        {% include "card-producto.njk" %}
        {% endfor %}
      </product-list>
    </div>
  </div>

</main>
